00:21:10,937 --> 00:21:12,105
ENCIK GA WOO-SU

341
00:21:12,188 --> 00:21:15,441
TINGGI GADIS MURIM
PEJABAT GURU DARJAH 11

342
00:21:36,963 --> 00:21:39,298
JADUAL WAKTU KESUSASTERAAN KOREA

343
00:21:41,926 --> 00:21:43,428
Adakah anda sedang mewarna?

344
00:21:45,054 --> 00:21:47,098
Ia supaya saya tidak keliru.

345
00:21:52,478 --> 00:21:53,312
Adakah anda berasa tidak selesa?

346
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:54,939
Mahukan antacid?

347
00:21:55,523 --> 00:21:58,026
Tidak, saya akan baik-baik saja.

348
00:22:17,211 --> 00:22:18,421
Adakah anda membasmi kuman?

349
00:22:19,088 --> 00:22:20,298
Jangan pelik sangat.

350
00:22:20,381 --> 00:22:21,340
Punggung keluar.

351
00:22:23,551 --> 00:22:25,178
Di dalam hutan tempat kerja,

352
00:22:25,261 --> 00:22:27,597
